        kit</a> to Oracle9iAS.</font> </p>
      <p><b><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Wireless and Voice 
        Made Easy With Oracle9i Application Server</font></b> <font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><br>
